\id 1JN - Zyphe
\h 1 JOHAN
\toc1 JOHAN CAKUA UIKHEHNAH
\toc2 1 JOHAN
\toc3 1 Jh
\mt1 JOHAN
\mt2 CAKUA UIKHEHNAH
\c 1
\s1 Hringnah bia
\p 
\v 1 Ahrangtho ning taitah a za ung thahpaw, a kong khah ca kaa cakuapaw he a cang. Ma cawh Hringnah Bia cang ka kaa naw tah thui ka, kaa meh tah hmuh ka, ming peh ka kaa kih tah a tawng thah.
\v 2 Hringnah cawh a va paly. Kaaning tah ma cawh hmuh he peh ka, a dawkhui he peh ka, Paw khatah ung katei, kaaning kha a za palypaw chaizaw hringnah cawh naaning khatah kaa y khui hi.
\v 3 Kaa hmuhpaw le kaa thuipaw khah naaning khatah kaa y khui, ma pawsui co kaaning khatah na pakong khy hrá he ceh. Taico ka huikongnah pawhe peh cawh Paw le a Sawcapaw Zisu Khri khatei a huikongnah khah a cang.
\v 4 Ka lawngnah pawhe peh tlingsah rua pawtah ma ca heh kaa ca kuapaw he a cang.
\s1 Khainah chung letah cinglai
\p 
\v 5 Ma bia heh a Sawcapaw taitah thui he peh katei, naaning kaa ca chingpaw he cawh a cang. Khazing cawh khainah cang ka, Ama a chung leco muinah zehmai ung be.
\v 6 Ama khatah a huikongnah kaa hnui tah he peh katei, muinah chung letah kaa cinglai thlang thly caco, hing he peh ka, biahmuisui letah ung bei peh tahnah a cang.
\v 7 Canghrasala Ama cawh khainah chung letah a ungpaw hratah kaaning zong khainah chung letah kaa cinglai caco, pakheh le pakheh a huikongnah hnui he peh ka, a Sawcapaw Zisu thihnah thisai tah kaaning cawh suanah vytei taitah a ma pathaisá a.
\p 
\v 8 Kaaning tah suanah hnui bei peh kaa tah caco, kaaning le kaaning a dungkheipaw cang he peh ka, kaa chung letah biahmuisui ung be tahnah a cang.
\v 9 Kaa suanah kaa phy caco, Ama cawh zingchuipaw le a dingpaw cang ka, kaa suanah sahlo khah ma ngethai ka, dinglynah vytei taitah a ma pathaisá a.
\v 10 Sua bei peh kaa tah caco, Khazing cawh mehing tah tua peh ka, a bia cawh kaa hringnah chung letah hminghmaw hnui be tahnah a cang.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Ka dopaw sawtei sahlo, naa sua ly nápaw cawtah ma ca heh ka ca kua he hi! Canghrasala pakheh kheh tah suanah a tua caco, Paw khatah a dawcakainah bia a ma reikaipaw Zisu Khri a dingpaw pakheh cawh kaa hnui thlang.
\v 2 Ama cawh kaa sua ngethainah cawtah a thuihlainah tah cang ka, kaaning kaa suanah caw long tah cang lytah khazaw pungpaluh suanah caw zong tah a cang hrah.
\p 
\v 3 A biapeh kaa nge caco, Ama kaa hni myca tah cawh kaa hni.
\v 4 Ama cawh ka hni thlang tah katei, a reipaw a tua tlung lypaw cawngsaw cawh mehing cang ka, biahmuisui cawh a chung letah ung be.
\v 5 Canghrasala pakheh kheh tah Ama a bia a nge caco, Khazing donah cawh a chung letah a tlangtling teitah a ung hmuisui. Ma heh Ama a chung letah ka ung he peh tah kaa hni nápaw cawh a cang:
\v 6 Khazing a chung letah ka ung aa tahpaw maikaw taco, Zisu Khri a hringzia hratah aa hring ruapaw a cang.
\p 
\v 7 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, naaning khahei phungbia a thapaw va cia bei neh, athoning taitei naa za thui thahpaw, a paringpaw tukhah a cang hri. Ma phungbia a paringpaw heh cawh naa za thui thahpaw bia khah a cang.
\v 8 Ma duitei cawh naaning khatah phungbia athapaw hratah va cia neh ka, a hmuisuipaw cawh Khri letah le naaning letah hmuh khy a cang, zecawtamaw tatah muinah cawh khung myca ka, khainah hmuisuipaw cawh a khai thahnah cawtah hei a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Khainah chung letah ka ung tah katei, a uny khah a hua thlangpaw cawh muinah chung letah a ungning thlangpaw a cang.
\v 10 A uny a dopaw cawh khainah chung letah ung ka, a chung letah ama a pachihly sápaw hming zehmai ung be.
\v 11 Canghrasala a uny a huapaw cawh muinah chung letah ung ka, muinah chung letah a cinglaipaw a cang; muinah taco a meh a cosah thahnah cawtah zelang maw a seilai leimei tahpaw khah hnih be.
\q1 
\v 12 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, Zisu a ming thongtah naa suanah vytei
\q2 ngethai a cang thah cawtah hei naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\q1 
\v 13 Paw sahlo, athoning taitah ahomaw a ung tahpaw
\q2 naa hni thahnah cawtah naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\q1 Mehny sahlo, naaning tah mehchaw lypaw Setan khah
\q2 naa te thahnah cawtah naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\q1 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, Paw khah naa hni thahnah cawtah
\q2 naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\q1 
\v 14 Paw sahlo, Ama cawh athoning taitah a ungpaw
\q2 a cangpaw khah naa hni thah cawtah naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\q1 Mehny sahlo, chong he ceh ka, Khazing bia naa chung letah
\q2 a ungnah cawtah le mehchaw lypaw Setan khah naa te thahnah cawtah
\q2 naaning khatah ma ca heh ka va ciapaw a cang.
\s1 Khazaw heh tlechai khe lo
\p 
\v 15 Khazaw heh tlechai khe la, a chung letei a ungpaw hming heh tlechai khe o. Pakheh kheh tah khazaw heh a tlechai caco, Paw donah cawh a chung letah ung be.
\v 16 Zecawtamaw tatah khazaw hming maikaw, ngaisaw dunah, mehthinah, hnui rungnah le tuasenah a palaikhuinah sahlo heh Paw taitah a chuhpaw cang bei he, khazaw taitah a chuhpaw a cang hri he.
\v 17 Khazaw le a dunah cawh a ly leimei myca, canghrasala Khazing dunah a tuapaw cawngsaw cawh chaizaw tah a hring a.
\s1 Khri a caraepaw sahlo a carae rua pawtah raering pehnah
\p 
\v 18 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, ma heh a hningcaipaw cai cang ka Khri a caraepaw a vong leimei tah naa thui thahpaw hratah Khri a caraepaw mehlupui cawh ato lehei hmai a chuh thah he. Ma heh a hningcaipaw cai a cang tah kaa hni nápaw cawh a cang.
\v 19 Aaning cawh kaa hrong taitah a chuhly he; canghrasala kaa cawngsaw cang hmuisui bei he. Zecawtamaw tatah kaa cawngsaw aa cang caco, kaaning khatah a ung thlang he a; canghrasala aa piathlahnah pawtah hei ahohmai kaa cawngsaw aa cang lypaw khah a langsah thlang.
\p 
\v 20 Canghrasala naaning cawh Mehpathaipaw tei sathy a thupaw cang he ceh ka, naa dawngkasawny tah biahmuisui cawh naa hni.
\v 21 Biahmuisui naa hnilynah cawtah naaning khatah ca ka va ciapaw cang lytah biahmuisui cawh hnih he ceh ka, biahmuisui taitah hinghenah a chua lynah cawtah a cang hri
\v 22 Ahomaw hingbia a reipaw cawh a cang? Zisu cawh Khri cang be, tatei a tahpaw cawngsaw khah a cang. Ma cawngsaw khah Khri a caraepaw cawh a cang kho, ama taco Paw kha Saw kha a hlawh he.
\v 23 Sawcapaw a hlawh paw taco Paw zong khah a hlawh; Sawcapaw a cyhlangpaw cawngsaw taco Paw zong khah a hni.
\p 
\v 24 Ahrangtho ning taitah naa za thuipaw khah naa chung letah paria thlang my lo. Ma hratei a cang caco, naaning zong Sawcapaw le Paw chung letah na ung he ceh.
\v 25 Taico ma heh Ama tei bia a ma kangpaw cawh a cang, chaizaw hringnah heh.
\p 
\v 26 Naaning lang pavesah a ca pachiapaw sahlo he aa kong khah ca tah naaning kha ka va cia hi.
\v 27 Naaning naa caw taco, Ama taitah naa hmuhpaw sathy thunah khah naa chung letah ung thlang ka, naaning cawngpah pawtah ahohmai hia khawh bei ceh. Canghrasala, Ama sathy a ca thunah pawhe tah zezongpui a ca cawngpah he, ma sathy thunah cawh ahmangpaw a cang, a pakheipaw cang be. Macawtaco a ca cawngpah pawhe hrakhei Ama a chung letah ung my lo.
\s1 Khazing sawtei sahlo
\p 
\v 28 Taico dopaw sawtei sahlo, Ama a chung leco ung thlang my lo, ma pawsui co, Ama a va lang kaw tihtah a hme letah kaa raechá ka, ningzaw lytah kaa ung khy hi.
\p 
\v 29 Ama cawh a dingpaw a cang takhah naa hni caco, a dingpaw hming a tuapaw maikaw he cawh Khazing taitah a pipaw a cang he takhah naa hni.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Paw tei kaa cung letah donah a hnuipaw heh zetlua tamaw a lai! Ma rawng taco Khazing sawtei sahlo tatah y kaa cang hi. Taico ma cawh kaa cangnahpaw cawh a cang. Khazaw tei a ma hnilynah a rawng cawh Ama a za hni lynah rawng tah a cang.
\v 2 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, atoheh kaaning sahlo cawh Khazing sawtei cang he peh ka, zemaw kaa va lo tae a tah duitei cawh a hnih balang be. Canghrasala Khri a lang tihtah Ama hratah ka cang tae peh tah cawh kaa hni, zecawtamaw tatah Ama cawh a cangnah ningtei hratah kaa hmuh a cawtah.
\v 3 Ama letei, ma hnabeisuinah a hnuipaw maikaw taco, Zisu Khri a pathaipaw hratah a pathai teitah aa ung.
\p 
\v 4 A suapaw maikaw taco phungbia khah aa ro; A hmuisui teico, sua tahpaw cawh phungbia hratei ung ly khah a cang.
\v 5 Canghrasala Khri cawh kaa suanah lah pah hly rua pawtah a vongpaw a cang takhah naa hni. Taico Ama a chung leco suanah ung be.
\v 6 Ama a chung letah a ungpaw cawngsaw cawh sua leimei bei he. Suanah a tua leimei thlangpaw cawngsaw taco Ama khah hmuh be ca ka, hnih hrah be.
\p 
\v 7 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, ahohmai a dungkheisah khe lo. A dingpaw hming a tuapaw cawngsaw cawh Khri a dingpaw hratah a ding hrah.
\v 8 A suapaw hming a tuapaw cawngsaw cawh Setan tei a cang, zecawtamaw tatah Setan cawh a hrangthoning taitah a sua leimeipaw a cang. Khazing Sawcapaw a vongnah a rawng cawh Setan a rai ro rua pawtah a cang.
\v 9 Khazing chung taitah a chuhpaw cawngsaw taco suanah khah tua paria thlang be, zecawtamaw tatah a chung lekhei Khazing thleci a ung; suanah letah sei leimei khy be, zecawtamaw tatah Khazing taitah a chuhpaw a cangnah cawtah a cang.
\v 10 Ma heh Khazing sawtei sahlo le Setan sawtei sahlo kaa binah pawhe cawh a cang: Adingpaw hming a tua lypaw cawngsaw a cang ly leh a uny a do lypaw cawngsaw cawh Khazing sawtei cang be.
\s1 Pakheh le pakheh a do my lo
\p 
\v 11 Ma heh a hrangthoning taitei naa za thuipaw bia khah a cang: Pakheh le pakheh ka do he peh tahpaw heh.
\v 12 Mehchaw lypaw Setan a tei cang katei, a uny a thehpaw Kain hratah cang khe lo. Taico zecawtamaw ama cawh a thaw? Zecawtamaw tatah ama a tuasanah cawh a suapaw cang ka, a unypaw a tuasanah cawh a dingpaw a cangnah cawtah a cang.
\v 13 Ka uny sahlo, khazaw tah a ca hua caco he, naa khuarawh chia kheh seh.
\v 14 Thihnah taitah hringnah lang kaa pange myca tah cawh kaa hni, zecawtamaw tatah kaa uny sahlo khah kaa donah caw he tah a cang. A uny a do lypaw cawngsaw cawh thihnah letah a ungpaw a cang.
\v 15 A uny a huapaw cawngsaw cawh lee a nongpaw cang ka; lee a nongpaw cawh a chung letah chaizaw hringnah hnui be takhah naa hni.
\p 
\v 16 Khri tah kaa cawtah a hringnah a peh cawtah donah hmuisui cawh zemaw a cang tah cawh kaa hni. Ma hraco kaa uny sahlo cawtah kaaning zong kaa hringnah kaa peh hrápaw a cang.
\v 17 Cawngsaw pakheh cawh hming le bo hnui ngetei ka, a unypaw a byhia khah a hmuh tihtah a cung letah ningdonah a hnui ly caco, Khazing donah a chung letah zekhatamaw a ung thai a?
\v 18 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, ka donah he peh cawh rei le kaw tah cang lytah biahmuisui le tuasená tah a cang hri ruapaw a cang.
\v 19 Ma cawh kaa tua tihtah biahmuisui letah kaa ung tah hnih peh ka, kaa lungthing tah sua a ma phosah tahmai tah a hmekaw letah lung khaitlawng teitah kaa ung.
\v 20 Zecawtamaw tatah Khazing cawh kaa lungthing navy tah lai vy ka, zezongpui khah a hni.
\p 
\v 21 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, kaa lungthing tah sua a ma phosah ly caco, Khazing hme letah raechahnah hnui peh ka,
\v 22 kaa haepaw maikaw cawh Ama taitah kaa hmuh. Zecawtamaw tatah a biapeh sahlo nge he peh ka, Ama a lawng sahpaw hming kaa tua cawtah a cang.
\v 23 Taico, ma heh a bia pehpaw cawh a cang. A Sawcapaw Zisu Khri a ming zing le Ama tei bia a ma pehpaw hratah pakheh le pakheh a do khah a cang.
\v 24 A biapeh a ngepaw sahlo cawh a chung letah ung he ka, Ama zong aa chung letah a ung hrah. Taico ma heh kaa chung letah a hring tah kaa hninahpaw cawh a cang. Ama tei a ma pehpaw Thlawpaw thongtah kaa hnipaw a cang.
\c 4
\s1 Thlawpaw pasenah
\p 
\v 1 Dopaw vesaw sahlo thlawpaw maikaw khah zing khe la, Khazing taitei a cang he maw tah hninah cawtah khei ma thlawpaw sahlo cawh pase my lo, zecawtamaw tatah khuavang pakheipaw a hlupui khazaw letah aa chua thahnah cawtah hei.
\v 2 Ma heh Khazing Thlawpaw a cang tah naa bi khy nápaw cawh a cang hi: Zisu Khri cawh mehnung pung tah a vong tatei a tahpaw thlawpaw maikaw cawh Khazing taiteipaw a cang he,
\v 3 canghrasala Zisu Khri cawh mehnung pung tah a vong be, tatei a tahpaw thlawpaw maikaw cawh Khazing taiteipaw cang bei he. Ma heh Khri a caraepaw thlawpaw a vong ka, atoheh khazaw letah a ung thah tatei naa thui thahpaw khah a cang.
\p 
\v 4 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, naaning sahlo cawh Khazing taiteipaw cang he ceh ka, a pakheipaw thlawpaw sahlo cawh naa te thah he, zecawtamaw tatah naaning letah a ungpaw cawh khazaw letei a ungpaw navy tah a thaw a tlung vy rong tah a cang.
\v 5 Aaning sahlo cawh khazaw leteipaw cang he ka, macawtaco khazaw hming kong khah aa rei. Khazaw tah aa rei khah a nge.
\v 6 Kaaning cawh Khazing taiteipaw cang he peh ka, Khazing a hnihpaw maikaw taco kaa bia khah aa nge hi; canghrasala Khazing taitei a cang lypaw maikaw taco kaa bia khah nge bei he. Ma heh biahmuisui Thlawpaw le thlawpaw pakheipaw kaa bikhynah cawh a cang.
\s1 Khazing donah le kaa tei
\p 
\v 7 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, donah cawh Khazing taitah a va chuhpaw a cangnah cawtah pakheh le pakheh a do he peh. Donah a tuapaw maikaw cawh Khazing taitah a pipaw cang he ka, Khazing khah aa hni.
\v 8 Donah a tua lypaw maikaw taco Khazing khah hnih bei he, zecawtamaw tatah Khazing cawh donah a cangnah cawtah.
\v 9 Ma heh Khazing tei kaa hrong letah a donah a lang sahnah cawh a cang: Khazing tah a Sawcapaw a hnuitlakangpaw khah khazaw letah a za thlawpaw cawh Ama a thongtah hringnah kaa hnui khy nápaw cawtah a cang.
\v 10 Ma heh donah cawh a cang. Khazing kaa dopaw heh cang be, canghrasala Ama tu tah ma do katei, kaa sua ngethainah a thuihlainah cawtah a Sawcapaw a za thlawpaw tuheh a cang hri.
\v 11 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, Khazing tei a ma dopaw hrahei kaaning zong pakheh le pakheh ka do ruapaw he peh a cang.
\v 12 Ahotahmai Khazing cawh hmuh bang bei he; canghrasala pakheh le pakheh ka do caco he peh, Khazing cawh kaaning letah ung ka, a donah cawh kaa chung letah a tling tahnah a cang.
\p 
\v 13 Khazing a chung letah ung he peh ka, Ama zong kaa chung letah a ung hrah tah cawh kaa hni, zecawtamaw tatah a Thlawpaw a ma peh cawtah hei a cang.
\v 14 Taico kaa hmuhpaw le kaa dawkhuipaw he peh cawh Paw tah a Sawcapaw cawh khazaw Pachahtu rua pawtah a za thlaw tahpaw heh a cang.
\v 15 Pakheh kheh tah Zisu cawh Khazing Sawcapaw a cang, a tah caco a chung letah Khazing ung ka, ama zong Khazing chung letah a ung hrah.
\v 16 Macawtaco kaa caw a cang cápaw Khazing donah cawh hnih he peh ka, ma leco ka pahnia he peh.
\p Khazing cawh donah a cang. Donah letei a ungpaw maikaw cawh Khazing chung letah ung he ka, aa chung letah Khazing a ung hrah.
\v 17 Ma hrahei donah cawh kaa hrong letah tlangtlingsah a cang myca, ma pawsui co biacenah ning letah hnawngangnah kaa hnui khy a, zecawtamaw tatah khazaw lehei Ama hratah kaa ung cawtah hei a cang.
\v 18 Donah leco cinah ung be. Canghrasala a tlangtlingpaw donah taco cinah khah a tingchua, zecawtamaw tatah cinah cawh dangtahnah khatah rai a hrehruipaw a cang he. Cinah a hnuipaw cawngsaw cawh donah letah a tlangtling lypaw a cang.
\p 
\v 19 Kaa dopaw cawh a ma do taw cawtah a cang.
\v 20 Pakheh kheh tah, Khazing ka do tah seh la, a uny a hua thlang tlung caco, ama cawh mehing a cang. Zecawtamaw tatah a hmuhpaw a uny hmai a do lypaw cawngsaw taco a hmuh lypaw Khazing cawh do khy a be.
\v 21 Taico kaaning cawh ma biapeh heh a ma peh thah. Khazing a dopaw cawngsaw taco a uny zong a do hrahring a tahpaw heh.
\c 5
\s1 Khazing sawcapaw letah zingnah
\p 
\v 1 Zisu cawh Khri a cang tatei a zingpaw maikaw cawh Khazing taitah a pipaw a cang he, Paw a dopaw maikaw taco a sawtei sahlo zong khah aa do he.
\v 2 Ma heh Khazing sawtei sahlo kaa do he tah kaa hninahpaw cawh a cang. Khazing do he peh katei, a biapeh kaa zuipaw heh.
\v 3 Ma heh Khazing do cawh a cang: A biapeh nge heh. A biapeh cawh kaa cawtah hmingrih cang be,
\v 4 zecawtamaw tatah Khazing taitah a pipaw maikaw taco khazaw heh aa te khy. Kaa zingnah cawh khazaw cung letah tenah a hnuipaw a cang.
\v 5 Ahomaw khazaw cawh a te khy? Zisu cawh Khazing Sawcapaw a cang tatei a zingpaw longlong tahei aa te khy.
\p 
\v 6 Tui le thisai khatei a vongpaw cawh Zisu Khri heh a cang. Ama cawh tui longtei khatah a vong be, tui le thisai khatah a vong hri. Taico, ma a dawkhuipaw cawh Thlawpaw heh a cang; zecawtamaw tatah Thlawpaw cawh biahmuisui a cang cawtah.
\v 7 Ma a dawkhuipaw heh sangthung a cang he:
\v 8 Thlawpaw, tui le thisai tahpaw cang he ka, aa sangthung hei aa bia a rua.
\v 9 Cawngsaw a dawkhuinah cawh kaa pawng, canghrasala Khazing a dawkhuinah cawh a lai vy, zecawtamaw tatah ma heh Khazing tei a Sawcapaw kong letah a reipaw a dawkhuinah cawh a cang.
\v 10 Khazing Sawcapaw a zingpaw taco a lung chung letah ma a dawkhuinah bia heh a hnui, a zing lypaw taco Khazing cawh a hingsah, zecawtamaw tatah Khazing tei a Sawcapaw kong letah a reipaw a dawkhuinah bia cawh a zing lynah cawtah a cang.
\v 11 Mataico, ma heh a dawkhuinah bia cawh a cang: Khazing tah kaaning cawh chaizaw hringnah ma pei thah ka, ma hringnah cawh a Sawcapaw chung letah a ung tahpaw heh.
\v 12 Khazing Sawcapaw a hnuipaw taco hringnah khah a hnui; Khazing Sawcapaw a hnui lypaw taco hringnah khah hnui be.
\s1 A changnah tei bia pataipaw
\p 
\v 13 Naaning Khazing Sawcapaw ming a zingpaw sahlo khatei ma hming sahlo kong ka ciapaw heh chaizaw hringnah naa hnui thah tah naa hni khy nápawtah a cang hi.
\v 14 Ma heh Khazing kaa pange ngangnah cawh a cang: A dunah hratah hming sangkheh kheh kaa hae caco, a ma thui a.
\v 15 Taico a ma thui a tah kaa hni caco Ama letei kaa haepaw maikaw khah kaa hnui thah tah kaa hni.
\p 
\v 16 Pakheh kheh tah a uny tei thihnah tai a phah khui lypaw suanah a tuapaw khah a hmuh caco, thlawchang seh la, Khazing tah hringnah a pae a. Aa suanah tei thihnah a phah khui lypaw sahlo cawtah ka reihnangpaw a cang. Thihnah a phahkhuipaw suanah a ung. Ma kong lehei thlaw naa chang a, ka tah dupaw cang be.
\v 17 Hmingchahly tuapaw vytei heh sua cang ka, canghrasala thihnah tai a phah khui lypaw suanah a ung.
\p 
\v 18 Khazing sawtei cawh sua canei leimei thlang be tah kaa hni; Khazing Sawcapaw takhei a bingsah ka, mehchaw lypaw Setan takhei hanah pei khy be.
\v 19 Kaaning cawh Khazing sawtei ka cang he peh tah le khazaw pungpaluh cawh mehchaw lypaw Setan a nawhnuinah rai letah a ung tah cawh kaa hni.
\v 20 Khazing Sawcapaw cawh a vong ka, ahmuisuipaw Khazing kha kaa hni khy ná pawtah hnithainah a ma peh tah cawh kaa hni. Kaaning cawh ahmuisuipaw Khazing le a Sawcapaw Zisu Khri chung letah kaa ung. Ama cawh Khazing hmuisui le chaizaw hringnah a cang.
\p 
\v 21 Dopaw sawtei sahlo, nono behnah taikhei naaning teitah a vai my lo.
